data.description: Welcome to the best of modern farmhouse living! This exceptional 4-bed, 3.5-bath custom home offers the perfect blend of modern comfort and rural lifestyle on 1.2 acres. At 3150 sq ft, this two-story abode features a spacious open layout, maximizing the abundance of natural light to create a warm and inviting feel. It's eye catching modern design features natural woods and clean geometric lines that you'll immediately fall in love with. On the main level you'll find a gourmet kitchen with professional line appliances, oversized island, and butler's pantry, an expansive main bedroom that opens to a luxurious spa-like bath with split vanities, a soaker tub, and large walk in closet, as well as a 2nd ensuite perfect for added privacy or guests. The upstairs space boasts 2 large bedrooms, full bath, and an expansive loft with wet bar that opens to a large covered balcony. The 40' RV garage, covered back patio perfect for gathering, and meticulously maintained lawn will be the envy of all your friends!
